<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 — Página no encontrada · Loop-Landing.com</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .err-wrap { min-height: 70vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; padding: 40px; }
    .err-code { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(6rem,18vw,14rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -6px; color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(0,210,255,0.25); position: relative; }
    .err-code::after { content: '404'; position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); font-size: inherit; filter: blur(20px); }
    .err-title { font-size: clamp(1.2rem,3vw,1.8rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin: 16px 0 12px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .err-sub { color: var(--text-2); font-size: 0.95rem; max-width: 380px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .err-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-slideshow">
  <div class="bg-slide" style="background-image:url('/img/jamesmarkosborne-code-1076536_1920.jpg')"></div>
  <div class="bg-slide" style="background-image:url('/img/fotis-fotopoulos-6sAl6aQ4OWI-unsplash.jpg')"></div>
  <div class="bg-slide" style="background-image:url('/img/pankaj-patel-Fi-GJaLRGKc-unsplash.jpg')"></div>
</div>
<canvas id="bg-canvas"></canvas>
<div class="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring"></div>

<%- include('./partials/lp-header', { user: locals.user }) %>

<div class="err-wrap">
  <div class="err-code">404</div>
  <h1 class="err-title">Página no encontrada</h1>
  <p class="err-sub">La ruta que buscás no existe o fue movida. Navegá de vuelta al inicio.</p>
  <div class="err-actions">
    <a href="/" class="lp-btn lp-btn-grad">← Volver al inicio</a>
    <a href="/portafolio" class="lp-btn lp-btn-ghost">Ver trabajos</a>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('./partials/lp-footer') %>

<script src="/js/particles.js"></script>
<script src="/js/menu-toggle.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
